    <string name="how_to_play_guide">%s GUIDE</string>
    <string name="snake_instructions">• Use D-PAD to move the snake.\n• Press UP/DOWN or MENU to change LEVEL.\n• LEVEL 1 has non-lethal warping walls!\n• Eat red apples to grow and score.</string>
    <string name="minesweeper_instructions">• Use D-PAD to move the cursor.\n• Press UP/DOWN or MENU to change LEVEL.\n• CENTER to reveal, MENU or \'S\' to flag.\n• Clear all safe cells to win.</string>
    <string name="game_4096_instructions">• Use D-PAD to slide tiles.\n• Tiles with same numbers merge.\n• Reach the 4096 tile to win!\n• Game ends when the board is full.\n• Press CENTER to restart if stuck.</string>
    <string name="game_trex_instructions">• Press UP or CENTER to jump.\n• Use characters for special abilities.\n• MENU, [M] or [O] for OPTIONS.</string>
    <string name="game_brick_break_instructions">• Move paddle with LEFT/RIGHT.\n• Press CENTER to launch ball or pause.\n• Break all bricks to clear the stage.\n• You have 3 lives. Don\'t let the ball fall.\n• Press \'S\' or MUTE to toggle sound.</string>
    <string name="game_tictactoe_instructions">• Move cursor with D-PAD.\n• Press CENTER to place X.\n• Beat the CPU by matching a row.\n• Turn alternates each match.\n• Change Board Size (3x3, 4x4, 5x5)\n  with UP/DOWN when Game Over\n  or press MENU any time.</string>
    <string name="game_checkers_instructions">• D-PAD: move cursor. CENTER: select square, then destination.\n• Red (you) moves up; CPU moves down. Dark squares only.\n• Captures are mandatory when possible; finish multi-jumps on the same piece (magenta outline).\n• Reach the far row to crown a king (K); kings slide and capture on all diagonals.\n• Clear all CPU pieces or block their moves to win.</string>
    <string name="game_sokoban_instructions">• D-PAD: move. Push boxes ($) onto targets (cyan rings); on-target shows as *.\n• Only one box at a time; you cannot pull.\n• CENTER: restart current level if stuck.\n• When a level is solved, CENTER advances. Clear all levels for a high score.</string>
    <string name="game_sudoku_instructions">• D-PAD to move. CENTER to cycle numbers.\n• Press UP/DOWN or MENU to change LEVEL.\n• Fewer starting clues = Higher level.\n• Solve without row/column repeats.</string>
    <string name="game_tetris_instructions">• Move piece with LEFT/RIGHT.\n• Rotate with UP.\n• Soft drop with DOWN.\n• Hard drop with CENTER.\n• Press H or INFO to pause/guide.</string>
    <string name="game_starfighter_instructions">• Move ship with D-PAD.\n• Triple lasers fire automatically.\n• Destroy enemies to score.\n• Collect green power-ups to upgrade weapons (5, 7 guns).\n• Avoid enemy ships and red bullets!\n• Press \'S\' to toggle sound.</string>
    <string name="game_memory_instructions">• Navigate with DPAD.\n• Press UP/DOWN or MENU to change LEVEL.\n• CENTER to flip. Match all pairs to win.\n• Higher levels have more cards!</string>
    <string name="game_slide_puzzle_instructions">• Use DPAD to move cursor.\n• Press UP/DOWN or MENU to change LEVEL.\n• CENTER to slide tile. Reorder to win.\n• Higher level = more puzzle pieces!</string>
    <string name="game_mental_math_instructions">• Solve the math problem.\n• Use DPAD to select answer.\n• Press CENTER to confirm.\n• Be quick! Timer is running.\n• Wrong answer ends game.</string>
    <string name="game_froggy_instructions">• Cross the road and river.\n• Avoid cars on the road.\n• Jump on logs in the river.\n• Reach the top to score!\n• Use D-PAD to move.</string>
    <string name="game_simon_instructions">• Watch the sequence of colors.\n• Repeat it using the D-PAD:\n  - UP: Yellow\n  - RIGHT: Green\n  - DOWN: Red\n  - LEFT: Blue\n• Sequence gets longer each round!</string>
    <string name="game_tanks_instructions">• Control your tank with D-PAD.\n• Tank fires automatically.\n• Destroy enemy tanks.\n• Protect your BASE (the star).\n• Bricks can be destroyed.</string>
    <string name="game_word_quest_instructions">• Guess the 5-letter word in 6 tries.\n• Use D-PAD to navigate keyboard.\n• Press CENTER to select letter.\n• GREEN: Correct letter &amp; position.\n• YELLOW: Correct letter, wrong position.\n• GRAY: Letter not in word.</string>
    <string name="game_dungeon_instructions">• Navigate the dungeon with D-PAD.\n• Collect the GOLDEN KEY.\n• Reach the EXIT DOOR to advance.\n• AVOID RED SPIKES at all costs!\n• Levels get harder with more obstacles.</string>
    <string name="game_flappy_instructions">• Press CENTER to flap your wings.\n• Fly through the gaps in the pipes.\n• Don\'t touch the pipes or the ground!\n• Score 1 point for every pipe cleared.\n• Test your reflexes!</string>
    <string name="game_lines98_instructions">• Use D-PAD to move the cursor.\n• Press CENTER to select a ball, then press CENTER on an empty cell to move it.\n• Align 5 or more balls of the same color (horizontal, vertical, or diagonal) to score and clear them.\n• Each move that doesn\'t clear lines adds 3 new balls.\n• Game ends when the board is full.\n• Press \'S\' or MUTE to toggle sound.</string>
    <string name="game_solitaire_instructions">• Use D-PAD to move the cursor.\n• Press CENTER to select/pick up cards, and CENTER to place them.\n• Build foundations by suit from Ace to King.\n• Build tableaus by alternating color and descending rank.\n• Press \'S\' or MUTE to toggle sound.</string>
    <string name="game_road_racer_instructions">• Move Left/Right to avoid traffic.\n• Survive as long as you can!\n• Press Center to Start/Pause.</string>
    <string name="game_hangman_instructions">• Select letters to guess the word.\n• You have 6 attempts.\n• Press Center to Guess.</string>
